elops%20more%20advanced%20Shahed%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20small%20Ukrainian%20drone%20built%20to%20chase%20down%20and%20intercept%20other%20aerial%20systems%20has%20recently%20achieved%20a%20speed%20of%20400%20kmph%2C%20or%20248.5%20mph%2C%20Kyiv's%20digital%20transformation%20minister%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B400%20km%2Fh%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20speed%20reached%20by%20an%20interceptor%20drone%20powered%20by%20a%20motor%20from%20Motor-G%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Brave1UA%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funjammable-russian-drones-now-long-range-threaten-ukraine-supply-lines-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMykhailo%20Fedorov%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%20Brave1%20is%20Ukraine's%20defense%20innovation%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20velocity%20means%20that%20the%20interceptor%20can%20beat%20the%20official%20speed%20record%20for%20Formula%201%20racing%2C%20achieved%20by%20Valtteri%20Bottas%20in%202016%20at%20231.46%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20speed%20of%20248.5%20mph%20also%20allows%20the%20drone%20to%20nearly%20match%20the%20fastest%20high-speed%20trains%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Shanghai%20Maglev%2C%20for%20example%2C%20reached%20speeds%20of%20280%20mph%20during%20tests%20in%20October%2C%20but%20is%20commercially%20operated%20at%20186%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-interceptor-drones-air-defense-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emotor-powered%20interceptor%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20doing%20so%20with%20propellers%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20jet%20engines%20or%20high-thrust%20combustion%20systems%20that%20propel%20other%20vehicles%20to%20extreme%20speeds.%20Because%20interceptor%20drones%20are%20designed%20to%20destroy%20other%20drones%20at%20a%20low%20cost%2C%20Ukraine's%20manufacturers%20typically%20price%20them%20below%20%246%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%2