ay's%20AI%20funding%20frenzy%2C%20particularly%20among%20early-stage%20startups%20raising%20money%20at%20huge%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20startups%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20haven't%20even%20got%20going%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20yet%20are%20raising%20at%20%26quot%3Btens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20valuations%20just%20out%20of%20the%20gate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sort%20of%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20can%20that%20be%20sustainable.%20You%20know%2C%20my%20guess%20is%20probably%20not%2C%20at%20least%20not%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20drew%20a%20distinction%20between%20those%20sky-high%20seed%20rounds%20and%20the%20large%20tech%20companies%20pouring%20billions%20into%20AI%20infrastructure.%20There's%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20real%20business%26quot%3B%20underpinning%20Big%20Tech's%20valuations%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20%26quot%3Boverhyped%20in%20the%20short%20term%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bstill%20underappreciated%20in%20the%20medium%20to%20long-term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20said%20an%20%26quot%3Bover-correction%26quot%3B%20is%20imminent%20for%20any%20major%20technology%20shift%20like%20AI%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20goes%20from%20skepticism%20to%20obsession%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20started%20DeepMind%2C%20no%20one%20believed%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFast%20forward%2010%2C%2015%20years%2C%20and%20now%2C%20obviously%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20only%20thing%20people%20talk%20about%20in%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20swing%20often%20pushes%20valuations%20too%20far%20and%20too%20fast.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20an%20overreaction%20to%20the%20underreaction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20also%20said%20he%20isn't%20worried%20about%20whether%20AI%20is%20in%20a%20bubble%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20focused%20on%20his%20job.%20Google%20DeepMind%20builds%20