ng%2C%20though%20we%20found%20it%20not%20as%20bright%20as%20others%20on%20our%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272cc0d4e-b571-4c58-87c2-83d8411de16b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mile%20High%20Life%20Dog%20Raincoat%20packs%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20for%20its%20budget-friendly%20price.%20The%20waterproofing%20is%20highly%20effective%2C%20passing%20our%20soak%20test%20with%20flying%20colors.%20A%20mesh%20lining%20adds%20breathability%2C%20and%20the%20lightweight%20polyester%20material%20makes%20it%20a%20good%20option%20for%20warmer%2C%20wet%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20make%20no%20mistake.%20While%20this%20jacket%20cuts%20costs%2C%20it%20doesn't%20cut%20corners.%20It%20held%20up%20well%20to%20our%20durability%20tests%2C%20including%20yanking%20on%20the%20velcro%20straps%20and%20aggressively%20scratching%20it%20with%20a%20dinner%20fork.%20Our%20canine%20tester%2C%20Roo%2C%20a%2040-pound%20mixed-breed%20dog%2C%20also%20dragged%20it%20through%20thorny%20bushes%20for%20added%20quality%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tan%20dog%20wearing%20a%20bright%20blue%20raincoat%20patterned%20with%20yellow%20ducks%20stands%20on%20grass%20and%20autumn%20leaves%2C%20shown%20from%20the%20side%20in%20one%20photo%20and%20from%20above%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941702a04eda4732f2d9600%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20the%20Mile%20High%20Life%20Dog%20Raincoat%20doesn't%20offer%20as%20much%20coverage%20as%20our%20other%20recommendations%2C%20it's%20a%20durable%2C%20lightweight%20jacket%20that%20withstood%20our%20waterproofing%20and%20durability%20tests.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Holbrook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coat%20comes%20with%20some%20notable%20extras%2C%20including%20a%20leash%20hole%20at%20the%20collar%20with%20a%20protective%20flap%20to%20keep%20rain%20out%20and%20super-reflective%20stripes%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20spot%20in%20the%20dark.%20Our%20favorite%20feature%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20leg%20straps%2C%20which%20are%20both%20adjustable%20and%20removable.%20Since%20leg%20straps%20can%20sometimes%20be%20too%20tight%20or%20too%20loose%20and%20get%20in%20the%20way%2C%20we%20loved%20being%20able%20to%20adjust%20or%20remove%20them%20entirely%2C%20especially%20for%20bathroom%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20downsides%2C%20though.%20The%20coat%20doesn't%20fully%20cover%20the%20belly%20and%20shoulders.%20And%20you%20can't%20toss%20it%20in%20the%20wash%20when%20it%20gets%20dirty.%20It%20can%20only%20be%20spot-cleaned%20with%20a%20wet%20cloth%2C%20which%20requires%20a%20little%20extra%20elbow%20grease%20to%20get%20out%20deep-set%20mud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22383ed580-34a9-4de7-a0a1-10df8a92c078%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20coverage%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20coverage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hurtta%20Mudventure%20Dog%20Coat%20Eco%20offers%20the%20most%20coverage%20of%20all%20the%20raincoats%20we%20tested.%20Its%20high%20collar%20protects%20more%20of%20the%20neck%2C%20and%20the%20material%20drapes%20along%20the%20sides%20and%20down%20the%20back%2C%20falling%20around%20a%20cutout%20for%20the%20tail.%20The%20front%20provides%20extra%20coverage%20with%20a%20poncho-like%20flap%20over%20the%20chest%20and%20shoulders%2C%20and%20highly%20reflective%20strips%20on%20each%20end%20of%20the%20coat%20offer%20excellent%20visibility%20in%20low%20light%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20coat%2C%20the%20Hurtta%20Mudaventure%20Eco%20is%20surprisingly%20easy%20for%20dogs%20to%20move%20around%20in%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20lightweight%20design%20that%20doesn't%20impede%20movement.%20It%20does%20run%20big%2C%20so%20it's%20probably%20best%20to%20size%20down%20if%20your%20dog%20is%20between%20sizes.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20that%20it%20comes%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sizes%2C%20and%20the%20coat%20itself%20is%20highly%20adjustable.%20There%20are%20two%20drawstrings%20at%20the%20neck%20to%20shorten%20the%20collar%20and%20one%20at%20the%20back%20to%20take%20in%20the%20length.%20An%20adjustable%20strap%20also%20firmly%20cinches%20around%20the%20waist%20to%20keep%20the%20coat%20securely%20in%20place%20%E2%80%94%20but%20almost%20too%20securely.%20We%20found%20the%20clasp%20tough%20to%20open%20at%20first%20and%20needed%20to%20apply%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tan%20dog%20wearing%20a%20gray%20raincoat%20is%20shown%20standing%20on%20grass%2C%20smiling%20toward%20the%20camera%20in%20one%20photo%20and%20facing%20away%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941706b64858d02d216dcf8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mudventure%20Dog%20Coat%20Eco%20is%20a%20lightweight%20raincoat%20that's%20designed%20for%20maximum%20coverage%20during%20rugged%20adventures.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Holbrook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20quality%20goes%2C%20you%20can%20see%20and%20feel%20that%20this%20coat%20is%20made%20of%20high-quality%2C%20durable%20materials.%20Roo%2C%20our%20most%20rambunctious%20tester%2C%20also%20put%20this%20one%20through%20the%20wringer%2C%20dragging%20it%20through%20thorns%20and%20bushes.%20The%20high%20quality%20does%20come%20at%20a%20high%20price%2C%20with%20the%20Mudventure%20Eco%20also%20taking%20the%20title%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20coat%20in%20our%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea5b3f6f-534f-47f9-b88a-c1b1bb034fbf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20large%20dogs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20large%20dogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOffering%20a%20similar%20design%20and%20coverage%20as%20the%20Hurtta%20Mudventure%20Eco%2C%20the%20Fjord%20Raincoat%202.0%20has%20additional%20sizes%20for%20larger%20dogs%2C%20with%20the%20biggest%20extending%2037.8%20inches%20in%20the%20back.%20Saril%20tested%20this%20one%20with%2070-pound%20German%20shepherd%20Davey%20and%20appreciated%20that%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20and%20secure%20a%20snug%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20adjustment%20points%3A%20two%20drawstrings%20at%20each%20end%20of%20the%20high-collared%20neck%2C%20an%20adjustable%20waistband%2C%20and%20a%20cinch%20point%20in%20the%20back%20by%20the%20tail%20%E2%80%94%20though%20we%20found%20that%20last%20one%20didn't%20do%20much%20to%20take%20up%20the%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20dog%20wearing%20an%20orange-and-black%20raincoat%20is%20shown%20outdoors%2C%20walking%20on%20a%20grassy%20yard%20while%20on%20a%20leash%20in%20one%20photo%20and%20viewed%20from%20behind%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694170c804eda4732f2d9614%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fjord%20Raincoat%202.0%20is%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20many%20large%20breeds%2C%20such%20as%20German%20shepherds%2C%20offering%20the%20largest%20size%20range%20among%20our%20top%20picks.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20generous%20sizing%20and%20adjustability%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20love%20about%20this%20sleek%20coat.%20The%20buttery-smooth%20material%20and%20four%20two-tone%20color%20options%20give%20it%20a%20polished%2C%20high-end%20look%2C%20while%20large%20reflective%20stripes%20and%20the%20logo%20provide%20high%20visibility%20during%20night%20walks%20or%20moody%20forest%20hikes.%20Drainage%20holes%20at%20the%20chest%20panel%20prevent%20water%20from%20collecting%20around%20your%20dog's%20belly%2C%20and%20leg%20straps%20keep%20everything%20in%20place.%20The%20hole%20for%20the%20harness%20is%20wide%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20attach%20the%20leash%2C%20and%20a%20flap%20of%20fabric%20prevents%20rain%20from%20dripping%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Mudventure%2C%20the%20Fjord%202.0%20is%20on%20the%20pricier%20side.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20two-year%20warranty.%20Non-stop%20dogwear%20also%20offers%20affordable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonstopdogwear.com%2Fproducts%2Fsj-duraflex-male-buckle%23product-description%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espare%20buckles%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20can%20buy%20in%20case%20yours%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294bd1b6d-c0e8-490c-aca8-1c1997775261%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20insulated%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20insulated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoft%20and%20warm%2C%20the%20Ruffwear%20Vert%20Waterproof%20Insulated%20Vest%20keeps%20dogs%20toasty%20without%20bogging%20them%20down%20with%20heavy%20insulation%20or%20a%20restrictive%20design.%20Like%20the%20Sun%20Shower%2C%20the%20vest-style%20Vert%20has%20a%20chest%20plate%20that%20buckles%20on%20each%20side%20of%20the%20belly%20to%20keep%20it%20dry.%20We%20found%20the%20fit%20snug%20and%20flexible%2C%20even%20for%20our%20medium-sized%20tester%2C%20Roo%2C%20whose%20broad%20chest%20is%20often%20difficult%20to%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vert's%20waterproofing%20is%20also%20excellent.%20It%20passed%20our%20soak%20tests%20easily%20and%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20protecting%20PNW-pup%20Roo%20on%20drizzly%20days.%20The%20coat%20also%20has%20a%20leash%20hole%20so%20dogs%20can%20wear%20it%20over%20their%20harness%20to%20keep%20it%20dry.%20However%2C%20the%20coat%20didn't%20fully%20cover%20the%20front%20of%20Roo's%20harness%2C%20causing%20the%20edges%20around%20the%20chest%20to%20dampen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tan%20dog%20wearing%20a%20bright%20blue%20raincoat%20stands%20on%20frosty%20grass%20in%20one%20photo%20and%20is%20seen%20from%20above%20while%20walking%20near%20autumn%20leaves%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69417104832e0ef1ead648c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ruffwear%20Vert%20allows%20dogs%20to%20enjoy%20cold%2C%20rainy%20days%20outdoors.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Holbrook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20confirm%20the%20coat's%20ability%20to%20retain%20heat%20on%20colder%20days%2C%20we%20conducted%20extra%20tests.%20Using%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20we%20filled%20it%20with%20water%20at%20100%20degrees%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20dog's%20body%20temperature.%20We%20then%20wrapped%20the%20coat%20around%20the%20water%20bottle%20and%20left%20it%20outside%20in%2045-degree%20weather%20for%2030%20minutes.%20After%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20we%20measured%20the%20water's%20temperature%20again%20and%20found%20it%20had%20only%20dropped%20to%2096%20degrees.%20For%20comparison%2C%20the%20same%20bottle%20left%20outside%20without%20a%20coat%20cooled%20to%2089%20degrees%2C%20an%2011-degree%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20in%20four%20different%20stylish%20two-tone%20colorways%20with%20reflective%20stripes.%20However%2C%20the%20stripes%20are%20not%20as%20vibrant%20as%20our%20other%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228921f1bc-48a6-409d-966c-663eeac32ff8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20raincoat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERaincoats%20differ%20widely%20in%20their%20fit%20and%20features.%20We%20asked%20our%20veterinarian%20experts%20what%20pet%20parents%20should%20look%20for%20when%20choosing%20a%20jacket%20for%20their%20dog's%20specific%20needs%20and%20body%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBoth%20Collins%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmedbiosci.colostate.edu%2Fdirectory%2Fmember%2F%3Fid%3Dalison-meindl-41390%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Alison%20Meindl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20clinical%20sciences%20at%20the%20Colorado%20State%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20and%20Biomedical%20Sciences%2C%20say%20proper%20fit%20is%20important%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20a%20raincoat%20for%20your%20dog.%20The%20coat%20shouldn't%20be%20too%20tight%20or%20too%20loose%2C%20and%20the%20leg%20openings%20should%20be%20large%20enough%20to%20prevent%20rubbing%20or%20friction%20on%20the%20dog's%20skin.%20To%20ensure%20a%20good%20fit%2C%20carefully%20measure%20your%20dog's%20back%20length%2C%20chest%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20drop%20size%20using%20a%20soft%20measuring%20tape%20and%20our%20guide%20below.%20Once%20you%20have%20your%20dog's%20measurements%2C%20compare%20them%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20size%20guide.%20When%20the%20coat%20is%20on%20your%20dog%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akc.org%2Fexpert-advice%2Flifestyle%2Fdog-raincoats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Kennel%20Club%20recommends%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20%26quot%3Btwo-finger%20slide%20test.%26quot%3B%20If%20you%20can't%20slide%20two%20fingers%20under%20the%20coat's%20straps%2C%20it's%20too%20tight%20and%20should%20be%20loosened.%20If%20you%20can%20slide%20three%20fingers%20under%2C%20it's%20too%20loose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIdeally%2C%20Collins%20says%20the%20coat%20should%20be%20adjustable%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20and%20take%20off%20your%20dog%20and%20stays%20in%20place%20while%20they%20wear%20it.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20says%20that%20the%20jacket%20should%20accommodate%20your%20dog's%20coat%20and%20body%20type.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20your%20dog%20has%20a%20broader%20chest%20or%20tends%20to%20puff%20up%20with%20extra%20winter%20floof%2C%20adjustable%20chest%20and%20belly%20straps%20are%20ideal.%20Smaller%20dogs%20may%20also%20find%20high%20rain%20collars%20inhibit%20their%20visibility%2C%20so%20adjustable%20necks%20can%20ensure%20they%20stay%20safe%20and%20comfortable.%20Collin%20adds%20that%20for%20all%20dogs%2C%20the%20coat%20shouldn't%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20potty%20breaks.%20Adjustable%20or%20removable%20leg%20straps%20help%20prevent%20any%20interference%2C%20and%20some%20coats%20even%20have%20a%20drawstring%20to%20adjust%20the%20back%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETightly%20woven%20fabrics%20like%20polyester%20and%20nylon%20are%20the%20most%20common%20materials%20for%20raincoats%2C%20with%20polyester%20slightly%20less%20absorbent%20and%20faster-drying%20than%20nylon.%20Polyester%20is%20also%20more%20breathable%2C%20which%20Meindl%20says%20is%20important%20to%20prevent%20your%20dog%20from%20overheating.%20These%20features%20make%20polyester%20well-suited%20for%20activities%20such%20as%20long-distance%20walks%20in%20the%20rain%20or%20during%20heavy%20downpours.%20Its%20breathability%20is%20also%20preferable%20for%20warm%2C%20rainy%20climates.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20nylon%20is%20stronger%20and%20more%20durable%2C%20making%20it%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20active%20dogs%20who%20enjoy%20hikes%20in%20the%20woods%20or%20adventures%20through%20rough%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20neither%20nylon%20nor%20polyester%20is%20completely%20waterproof.%20Both%20materials%20require%20an%20additional%20waterproof%20coating%20of%20either%20polyethylene%20(PU)%20or%20polyvinyl%20chloride%20(PVC)%20to%20be%20impervious%20to%20moisture.%20Raincoats%20made%20entirely%20of%20PVC%20are%20also%20available%20if%20you%20value%20water%20resistance%20over%20all%20else.%20This%20rubber-like%20material%20is%20completely%20waterproof%2C%20but%20it%20is%20stiffer%20and%20less%20breathable%20than%20nylon%20or%20polyester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeindl%20also%20recommends%20looking%20for%20reflective%20materials%20to%20make%20your%20dog%20more%20visible%20in%20low-light%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaterproof%20rating%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOutdoor%20brands%20use%20water-entry%20pressure%20tests%20to%20determine%20waterproof%20ratings%2C%20which%20is%20the%20point%20at%20which%20the%20fabric%20leaks.%20The%20higher%20the%20rating%2C%20often%20measured%20in%20millimeters%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20effectiveness.%20However%2C%20different%20brands%20have%20different%20ideas%20about%20what%20equates%20to%20waterproofing.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116842078mh-20%26h%3D45f96312a99f0c960038bd935919a2a4dcf9cdb3f7c098f06d46cfc2f6c53108%26postID%3D69415314c575b1006f849efa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-raincoats%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.rei.com%252Flearn%252Fexpert-advice%252Frainwear-how-it-works.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EREI%3C%2Fa%3E%20considers%202%2C109%20mm%20or%20higher%20to%20be%20rainproof%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruffwear.com%2Fblogs%2Fexplored%2Fwhats-the-difference-between-waterproof-water-resistant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuffwear%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20between%205%2C000%20mm%20and%2010%2C000%20mm%20is%20fully%20waterproof.%20Both%20brands%20agree%2C%20though%2C%20that%20wind-driven%20rain%20is%20equivalent%20to%201%2C400%20mm%20of%20pressure.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20can%20find%20a%20rating%20above%20that%2C%20you'll%20likely%20be%20okay.%20And%20if%20you're%20still%20unsure%2C%20GORE-TEX%20experts%20say%20that%20simulation%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20ones%20we%20conducted%20for%20this%20guide%20%E2%80%94%20can%20provide%20more%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDifferent%20raincoats%20will%20have%20different%20closures%20and%20attachment%20systems.%20%26quot%3BJackets%20may%20include%20features%20such%20as%20Velcro%2C%20buckles%2C%20snaps%2C%20zippers%2C%20and%20buttons%20%E2%80%94%20find%20what%20works%20best%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20says.%20For%20wiggly%20dogs%20who%20can't%20sit%20still%20or%20dislike%20things%20placed%20over%20their%20heads%2C%20Meindl%20recommends%20opting%20for%20a%20Velcro%20closure%20over%20snaps%20and%20zippers%20to%20speed%20things%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%20Instructions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20rainy%20walks%20often%20expose%20your%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20raincoat%20%E2%80%94%20to%20mud%20and%20grimy%20puddles%2C%20look%20for%20a%20coat%20that's%20easy%20to%20clean.%20Coats%20that%20can%20be%20thrown%20in%20the%20wash%20are%20more%20convenient%20for%20frequent%20use%20than%20ones%20that%20must%20be%20hand-washed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22185e401d-529b-46f7-883c-b0d87cde94cb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20first%20published%20this%20guide%20in%202021%20after%20freelance%20reporter%20and%20professional%20dog%20trainer%20Shoshi%20Parks%20interviewed%20dog%20walkers%20and%20a%20veterinarian%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20best%20raincoats.%20Due%20to%20dry%20weather%20and%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20restrictions%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20she%20could%20not%20test%20these%20jackets%20on%20dogs%20of%20multiple%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20in%20real%20rainy%20weather.%20Instead%2C%20she%20devised%20a%20few%20tests%20to%20simulate%20wet%20and%20muddy%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20freelance%20reporter%20Elizabeth%20Holbrook%20has%20conducted%20further%20testing%20on%20some%20of%20the%20same%20products%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20new%20options%20%E2%80%94%20by%20trying%20out%20medium-sized%20coats%20with%20her%2040-pound%20rescue%20mix.%20Additionally%2C%20deals%20editor%20Sarah%20Saril%20and%20her%2015-pound%20Chihuahua%2C%20along%20with%20senior%20home%20editor%20Jaclyn%20Turner%20and%20her%2020-pound%20pup%2C%20tried%20our%20small%20raincoat%20options.%20Saril's%2070-pound%20German%20shepherd%20also%20tested%20our%20large%20jacket%20contender.%20Along%20with%20assessing%20fit%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20waterproofing%20effectiveness%20by%20taking%20their%20dogs%20outside%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20weather%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20rainy%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20they%20used%20the%20tests%20below%20to%20make%20their%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFirst%2C%20we%20confirmed%20that%20the%20coat's%20actual%20measurements%20matched%20the%20advertised%20size%2C%20noting%20when%20the%20jacket%20fit%20more%20tightly%20or%20loosely%20than%20expected.%20Next%2C%20we%20evaluated%20how%20easy%20each%20coat%20was%20to%20put%20on%2C%20adjust%2C%20and%20take%20off.%20From%20there%2C%20we%20took%20our%20dogs%20on%20two%20walks%20or%20more%2C%20staying%20outside%20for%20at%20least%2010%20minutes%2C%20often%20much%20longer.%20We%20examined%20whether%20any%20part%20of%20the%20raincoat%20caused%20discomfort%20or%20restricted%20movement%2C%20including%20the%20dog's%20ability%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom.%20We%20also%20determined%20whether%20the%20coat%20provided%20full%20coverage%20or%20left%20key%20areas%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Upon%20unboxing%20the%20coats%2C%20we%20confirmed%20their%20quality%20and%20checked%20for%20any%20construction%20defects%2C%20such%20as%20flimsy%20material%20or%20broken%20seams.%20To%20test%20for%20durability%2C%20we%20tugged%20on%20buckles%2C%20zippers%2C%20and%20straps.%20We%20also%20operated%20zippers%20and%20Velcro%20closures%2020-plus%20times%20to%20ensure%20they%20wouldn't%20break%20easily%20with%20extended%20wear.%20For%20all%20coats%2C%20we%20used%20a%20dinner%20fork%20and%20pressed%20down%20as%20hard%20as%20possible%20to%20see%20if%20it%20caused%20any%20damage%20to%20the%20fabric%20or%20hardware.%20We%20also%20noted%20any%20changes%20in%20quality%20after%20our%20walks%20and%20adventures%20with%20our%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoak%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20waterproofing%20test%20evaluated%20how%20each%20raincoat%20would%20stand%20up%20under%20heavy%20rain.%20We%20also%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20the%20coat%20would%20start%20leaking%20after%20getting%20soaked%20at%20any%20point%20during%20a%20standard%2030-minute%20walk.%20To%20test%20this%2C%20we%20took%20a%20clean%2C%20dry%20towel%20and%20wrapped%20each%20coat%20around%20it%20before%20placing%20the%20coat%20on%20the%20top%20of%20a%20bucket%20in%20the%20shower.%20We%20then%20sprayed%20the%20coat%20for%20two%20minutes%20and%20let%20it%20sit%20in%20the%20shower%20for%2030%20minutes.%20Then%20we%20examined%20whether%20the%20towel%20and%20the%20coat's%20inner%20lining%20remained%20dry.%20We%20also%20noted%20if%20there%20was%20a%20considerable%20difference%20in%20the%20weight%20or%20temperature%20of%20the%20raincoat.%20To%20ensure%20the%20rain%20jackets%20didn't%20lose%20their%20waterproofing%20after%20washing%2C%20we%20repeated%20this%20test%20after%20completing%20our%20cleaning%20test%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20cleaning%20test%20consisted%20of%20three%20parts.%20First%2C%20we%20wiped%20a%20handful%20of%20mud%20on%20the%20exterior%20of%20each%20jacket%20and%20let%20it%20dry%20overnight.%20Next%2C%20we%20attempted%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20mud%20using%20a%20clean%2C%20dry%20cloth.%20Finally%2C%20we%20washed%20the%20raincoat%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%2C%20looking%20for%20any%20stains%20or%20other%20changes%20in%20the%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef482cbb-01b6-40dd-ae14-eebdc7a276cc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20raincoats%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20dogs%20wear%20raincoats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20dogs%20need%20a%20raincoat%2C%20and%20most%20dogs'%20fur%20should%20provide%20sufficient%20protection%20from%20the%20rain.%20However%2C%20Meindl%20and%20Collins%20say%20breeds%20with%20particularly%20short%20or%20thin%20coats%2C%20such%20as%20greyhounds%20and%20whippets%2C%20may%20appreciate%20the%20added%20rain%20barrier%20a%20coat%20provides.%20Collins%20adds%20that%20dogs%20with%20lean%20body%20conditions%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20become%20uncomfortable%20or%20chilled.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akc.org%2Fexpert-advice%2Flifestyle%2Fdog-raincoats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Kennel%20Club%20recommends%3C%2Fa%3E%20raincoats%20for%20senior%20dogs%2C%20whose%20bodies%20have%20less%20fat%20to%20insulate%20them.%20Lastly%2C%20Collins%20points%20out%20that%20some%20dogs%20should%20wear%20a%20raincoat%20simply%20because%20they%20don't%20like%20getting%20wet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20should%20your%20dog%20wear%20a%20raincoat%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20dog%20is%20experiencing%20an%20underlying%20health%20concern%2C%20Collins%20says%20a%20raincoat%20may%20help%20keep%20them%20comfortable%20and%20warm.%20%26quot%3BA%20raincoat%20will%20be%20useful%20for%20dogs%20that%20need%20to%20stay%20dry%20due%20to%20healing%20from%20a%20recent%20surgery%20or%20a%20skin%20problem%20that%20is%20under%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20For%20dogs%20with%20skin%20issues%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20prolonged%20periods%20of%20dampness%20can%20predispose%20them%20to%20bacterial%20or%20fungal%20infections.%20Collins%20also%20says%20that%20dogs%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20require%20a%20coat%20when%20the%20temperatures%20drop%20or%20when%20they're%20outside%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%20%26quot%3BDogs%20who%20are%20going%20outside%20for%20a%20quick%20potty%20break%20may%20not%20need%20a%20raincoat%20unless%20it%20is%20colder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20waterproof%20fabric%20for%20dog%20coats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPolyester%20and%20nylon%20are%20the%20most%20common%20fabrics%20used%20in%20dog%20raincoats%2C%20and%20both%20repel%20water%20effectively.%20That%20said%2C%20polyester%20is%20slightly%20less%20absorbent%2C%20resulting%20in%20faster%20drying%20times.%20It's%20also%20lighter%20and%20more%20breathable%20than%20nylon%2C%20which%20Meindl%20says%20is%20an%20important%20characteristic%20to%20prevent%20your%20dog%20from%20overheating.%20Nylon%20is%20slightly%20stronger%20and%20more%20abrasion-resistant%2C%20so%20it's%20better%20suited%20for%20dogs%20who%20enjoy%20hiking%20or%20rough%20play.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20for%20either%20material%20to%20be%20truly%20waterproof%2C%20an%20additional%20coating%20such%20as%20polyurethane%20(PU)%20or%20polyvinyl%20chloride%20(PVC)%20is%20required.%20Dog%20raincoats%20made%20entirely%20of%20PVC%20are%20also%20available.%20They%20offer%20complete%20protection%20against%20rain%2C%20but%20their%20minimal%20breathability%20isn't%20the%20best%20option%20for%20warmer%20weather%20or%20dogs%20with%20thicker%20coats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20a%20dog%20raincoat%20have%20a%20hood%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMeindl%20says%20there's%20no%20harm%20in%20dressing%20your%20dog%20in%20a%20hooded%20coat%20if%20they%20tolerate%20the%20hood%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20recommend%20them%20specifically.%20Matthew%20Condrin%2C%20professional%20dog%20walker%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbancanines.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrban%20Canines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20that%20while%20a%20hood%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20it%20can%20add%20more%20frustration%20than%20function.%20%26quot%3BThey%20annoy%20the%20dogs%20by%20sometimes%20covering%20their%20eyes%20and%20interfere%20with%20leashing%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20they%20rarely%20stay%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Condrin%20says.%20In%20freelance%20reporter%20Alex%20Rennie's%20experience%2C%20both%20his%20dogs%20tend%20to%20shake%20their%20hoods%20off%20during%20walks%2C%20and%20he%20finds%20them%20more%20restrictive%20than%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22822d4e29-4737-4b53-b2f2-35cdb55e19dd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20measure%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20raincoat%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20measure%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20raincoat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20come%20in%20so%20many%20different%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20that%20fitting%20one%20for%20a%20raincoat%20can%20be%20a%20lengthy%20process%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Since%20there's%20no%20universal%20sizing%20for%20canine%20apparel%2C%20what%20one%20brand%20considers%20small%20could%20easily%20be%20considered%20large%20by%20another%20brand.%20To%20get%20the%20right%20fit%2C%20grab%20a%20measuring%20tape%20and%20follow%20these%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20primary%20dimension%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20size%20of%20a%20raincoat%20is%20the%20length%20of%20a%20dog's%20back.%20Measure%20your%20dog%20from%20the%20base%20of%20their%20tail%20to%20their%20shoulder%20blades%20while%20they%20are%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position.%20If%20your%20measurement%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20size%20up.%20Some%20brands%20may%20recommend%20a%20specific%20size%20for%20certain%20breeds.%20This%20may%20be%20helpful%2C%20but%20don't%20rely%20on%20suggestions%20alone%2C%20as%20sizes%20can%20vary%20among%20a%20single%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChest%20girth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dog%20raincoats%20are%20also%20commonly%20measured%20by%20chest%20girth.%20This%20is%20an%20important%20figure%20to%20get%20right%20because%20many%20jackets%20are%20not%20adjustable%20around%20the%20chest.%20That's%20doubly%20true%20if%20you%20have%20a%20broad%20or%20barrel-chested%20pup.%20To%20get%20this%20figure%2C%20measure%20the%20circumference%20of%20your%20dog's%20chest%20while%20they're%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position%2C%20wrapping%20the%20tape%20right%20behind%20the%20legs%20at%20the%20chest's%20widest%20point.%20If%20your%20dog's%20chest%20girth%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20choose%20the%20larger%20option%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20dog%20does%20a%20lot%20of%20running%20and%20jumping.%20A%20highly%20active%20dog%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20jacket%20that%20is%20an%20inch%20or%20two%20wider%20than%20their%20actual%20measurement%20because%20it%20will%20allow%20their%20front%20legs%20more%20freedom%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeck%20girth%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20make%20sure%20your%20jacket%20won't%20be%20too%20tight%20around%20the%20neck%2C%20measure%20around%20the%20thickest%20part%20right%20below%20the%20collar.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20if%20the%20coat's%20neck%20lacks%20an%20adjustable%20opening.%20When%20in%20doubt%2C%20size%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrop%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Occasionally%2C%20brands%20offer%20a%20drop%20measurement%20to%20help%20you%20get%20the%20right%20fit.%20The%20drop%20is%20how%20low%20a%20jacket%20hangs%20on%20a%20dog's%20body%20and%20legs.%20If%20the%20measurement%20is%20too%20long%2C%20it%20may%20restrict%20movement%3B%20too%20short%2C%20and%20your%20pup%20may%20get%20wet%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20walk.%20Your%20dog's%20raincoat%20should%20extend%20at%20most%20halfway%20down%20the%20leg.%20To%20figure%20out%20how%20a%20jacket%20will%20lie%20on%20your%20dog%2C%20compare%20half%20its%20width%20to%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20top%20of%20your%20dog's%20tail%20to%20the%20ankle%20of%20their%20hind%20leg%20just%20above%20the%20paw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcbf0036-b55d-4ce5-ba29-c9f05f8cf408%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20walk%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20rain%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20walk%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20rain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20walks%20along%20a%20forest%20trail%20holding%20a%20leash%20as%20a%20small%20tan%20dog%20in%20a%20yellow%20raincoat%20trots%20beside%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941a3c104eda4732f2d9d4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReporter%20Elizabeth%20Holbrook%20walks%20Roo%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20the%20Ruffwear%20Sun%20Shower%20Dog%20Raincoat.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Holbrook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20dog%20hates%20leaving%20the%20house%20when%20the%20rain%20starts%20to%20fall%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20fitting%20them%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats%2C%20these%20tips%20for%20wet-weather%20walking%20will%20ensure%20that%20you%20meet%20their%20most%20important%20daily%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20the%20right%20gear%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20rainy%20day%20walks%20more%20enjoyable%20by%20getting%20your%20pup%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats.%20A%20properly%20fitted%20coat%20that%20covers%20both%20the%20chest%20and%20belly%20will%20prevent%20your%20dog%20from%20splashing%20water%20against%20the%20most%20sensitive%20parts%20of%20their%20body.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20sensitive%20paws%2C%20you%20may%20also%20want%20to%20consider%20getting%20a%20set%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-boots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20boots%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlan%20ahead%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unless%20the%20forecast%20calls%20for%20extreme%20weather%2C%20most%20rainy%20days%20have%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20periods%20in%20which%20showers%20slow%20to%20a%20sprinkle.%20Use%20a%20weather%20tracking%20app%20or%20website%20to%20help%20you%20predict%20when%20a%20storm%20will%20lighten%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncourage%2C%20don't%20force%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20if%20you%20have%20the%20proper%20rain%20gear%20for%20your%20pup%2C%20your%20dog%20may%20still%20avoid%20the%20rain%20at%20all%20costs.%20These%20dogs%20will%20likely%20require%20an%20extra%20incentive.%20Before%20getting%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20stuff%20your%20pockets%20full%20of%20treats%20and%20offer%20them%20before%20you%20step%20out%20the%20door.%20If%20putting%20on%20rain%20gear%20predicts%20that%20treats%20will%20follow%2C%20your%20dog%20will%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20allow%20you%20to%20get%20them%20dressed.%20Use%20your%20treats%20to%20entice%20your%20dog%20out%20the%20door%20instead%20of%20forcing%20them%20to%20go%20out%20into%20the%20rain%2C%20which%20will%20only%20make%20them%20more%20frightened%20and%20stressed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlay%20the%20%26quot%3BFind%20It%26quot%3B%20game%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Keep%20the%20treats%20flowing%20once%20outside.%20Try%20encouraging%20your%20dog%20to%20walk%20with%20the%20Find%20It%20game.%20Throw%20a%20treat%20a%20few%20feet%20in%20front%20of%20your%20dog%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bfind%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20happy%20tone.%20Let%20them%20gobble%20up%20the%20treat%2C%20then%20throw%20your%20next%20one%2C%20repeating%20the%20phrase.%20Play%20the%20game%20as%20much%20as%20necessary%20during%20the%20walk%20to%20get%20your%20pup's%20mind%20off%20the%20water%20falling%20from%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20expect%20a%20regular%20walk%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20with%20plenty%20of%20treats%20and%20encouragement%2C%20dogs%20who%20really%20hate%20the%20rain%20aren't%20likely%20to%20want%20to%20stay%20outdoors%20for%20long.%20If%20they%20go%20potty%20and%20then%20refuse%20to%20go%20any%20farther%2C%20that's%20OK.%20Bring%20them%20back%20inside%20and%20make%20up%20the%20missed%20exercise%20with%20play%20or%20indoor%20training.%20Read%20more%20on%20backup%20plans%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStick%20to%20quiet%20streets%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20rainy%20days%2C%20when%20cars%20zoom%20through%20puddles%2C%20the%20busier%20the%20street%2C%20the%20louder%20it%20will%20be.%20And%20the%20more%20noise%2C%20the%20more%20frightened%20your%20dog%20is%20likely%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20all%20that%20potential%20for%20being%20splashed%20by%20passing%20vehicles.%20When%20it's%20raining%2C%20stick%20to%20quieter%20streets%20where%20there%20is%20less